<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.1">
<l>kēca vaṉṟamar kīḻmē lemarēḻu piṟappu</l>
<l>mācati ritupeṟṟu nammuṭai vāḻvu vāykkiṉṟavā</l>
<l>vīca ṉeṉkaru māṇikkameṉ ceṅkōlak kaṇṇaṉ viṇṇōr</l>
<l>nāyaka ṉempirā ṉemmā ṉārāya ṇaṉālē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our people will through seven births before [and] after be Keśava’s people,</l>
<l>as our lives will flourish, having obtained this which is a great blessing</l>
<l>through the lord, my black ruby, my Kṛṣṇa of red beauty, the leader</l>
<l>of the celestials, our lord, our father, Nārāyaṇa.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
